mparison Tables</a></h2>\n<a href="http://www.webdesigndev.com/inspiration/25-clear-and-beautiful-comparison-tables"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-89" title="comparison-charts" src="http://dev.cameronbaney.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/comparison-charts.jpg" alt="comparison-charts" width="598" height="154" /></a>\n\nA showcase of 25 comparison tables. Great inspiration for your next project.\n\n<hr />\n<h2><a href="http://inspirationti.me/websites/design-agencies/">44 Amazing Agency Websites</a></h2>\n<a href="http://inspirationti.me/websites/design-agencies/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-85" title="44-creative-web" src="http://dev.cameronbaney.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/44-creative-web.jpg" alt="44-creative-web" width="598" height="154" /></a>\n\nAnother showcase of creative agency websites. This list includes graphic design and advertising agencies, and only repeats a few of the sites that were featured on Indeziner.\n\n<hr />\n<h2><a title="AutoSprites - A jQuery Menu Plugin" rel="bookmark" href="http://www.newmediacampaigns.com/page/autosprites-jquery-menu-plugin">AutoSprites - A jQuery Menu Plugin</a></h2>\n<a href="http://www.newmediacampaigns.com/page/autosprites-jquery-menu-plugin"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-88" title="autosprites" src="http://dev.cameronbaney.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/autosprites.jpg" alt="autosprites" width="598" height="154" /></a>\n\nA jQuery plugin that makes it easy to create animated menus using CSS sprite sheets.', 'Neat Tweets #2', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83-revision', '', '', '2009-11-02 15:35:51', '2009-11-02 20:35:51', '', 83, 'http://dev.cameronbaney.com/?p=488', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
